  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490140/extras/1a9c4102aaa9af7092e556c344f78f54.poster.avif?t=1723786313\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490140/extras/1a9c4102aaa9af7092e556c344f78f54.webm?t=1723786313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490140/extras/1a9c4102aaa9af7092e556c344f78f54.mp4?t=1723786313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join Floppy the frog in a wild jumping adventure! Your mission is to reach the top without falling or rage quit halfway through. Bounce on trampolines, jump on moving platforms, and tackle quick time events.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490140/extras/2445e4dc77b36121ead79d01a45eda87.avif?t=1723786313\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><strong>Challenging Obstacles:</strong> Navigate moving platforms, trampolines, and more.<br><strong>Fun Physics:</strong> Each jump is a thrill with unpredictable outcomes.<br><strong>Humorous Dialogues:</strong> Enjoy a collection of frog-themed jokes and witty dialogues that add a light-hearted touch to your adventure.<br><br>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490140/extras/1a9c4102aaa9af7092e556c344f78f54.poster.avif?t=1723786313\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490140/extras/1a9c4102aaa9af7092e556c344f78f54.webm?t=1723786313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490140/extras/1a9c4102aaa9af7092e556c344f78f54.mp4?t=1723786313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join Floppy the frog in a wild jumping adventure! Your mission is to reach the top without falling or rage quit halfway through. Bounce on trampolines, jump on moving platforms, and tackle quick time events.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490140/extras/2445e4dc77b36121ead79d01a45eda87.avif?t=1723786313\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><strong>Challenging Obstacles:</strong> Navigate moving platforms, trampolines, and more.<br><strong>Fun Physics:</strong> Each jump is a thrill with unpredictable outcomes.<br><strong>Humorous Dialogues:</strong> Enjoy a collection of frog-themed jokes and witty dialogues that add a light-hearted touch to your adventure.<br><br>",
